data.description: This beautiful 4 bedroom 3.5 bath colonial  located in the desired neighborhood of Hopyard Farms has just the right curb appeal to welcome you home! On a corner lot of .25 acres, it has a stone front entrance with a front porch, lovely shrubs and plants surrounding the landscape. The entrance way has lovely high ceilings, hardwood floors and a half bath on the first floor. Master suite has huge walk in closet, master bath with soaker tub and walk-in shower, laundry room is located on the first floor. There is an extra room in the basement that can be used as an office or extra bedroom. The bathroom in the basement is a full bath with a walk-in shower and handicap assisted bar. All stainless steel appliances in the kitchen and a (1) white stand up freezer in the garage that will not convey.  Washer/Dryer (white) in laundry room will convey. (Stainless Steel appliances in garage will not accept the stainless steel stand-up freezer).
